---
description: Tailwind usage & purge safety
globs:
  - "tailwind.config.{cjs,js}"
  - "src/**/*.{svelte,js}"
---

- Use utility classes; do not inline style unless necessary.
- Keep `content: ["./src/**/*.{svelte,js}"]` up to date.
- If generating dynamic class names (e.g., `grid-cols-${n}`), either hardcode valid values or add them to `safelist` in tailwind config.
- Do not remove classes from critical selectors without being asked.
